description:
Carry paddles, masts, booms and other lengthy equipment. Use the JawGrip to securely mount it to your car's roof rack.

  • Padded cradles protect your gear
  • Individually tightening straps for gear of different sizes
  • Works with Thule T-track mounting systems (square bar adapters available from Thule)
  • Holds gear up to 5.5cm in diameter
name: Thule JawGrip Multipurpose Holder
